epperton lock.\n\n==See also==\n{{Portal|United Kingdom|Transport}}\n*[[Locks on the River Thames]]\n*[[Rowing on the River Thames]]\n*{{Cite web |url= http://www.riverthames.co.uk/about_thames/3763.htm|title= Shepperton Lock|accessdate= 2009-01-08|publisher= The River Thames Guide}}\n\n{{S-start}}\n{{River lock start|River=[[River Thames]]}}\n{{River lock line|upstream=[[Chertsey Lock]]<br/>{{convert|3.32|km|abbr=on}} <ref name=\"EnvAgency2\" >{{cite web |url= http://www.environment-agency.gov.uk/homeandleisure/recreation/131811.aspx |title=Environment Agency Distances between locks on the River Thames |date=19 November 2012 |work=web page |publisher=Environmental Agency |accessdate=22 November 2012}} Distances given in km.</ref>|downstream=[[Sunbury Lock]]<br/>{{convert|4.75|km|abbr=on}}<ref name=\"EnvAgency2\" />|location= TQ0725465964}}\n{{S-end}}\n\n==Notes and references==\n;References\n{{reflist}}\n;Notes\n{{reflist|group=n}}\n\n{{Spelthorne}}\n\n[[Category:1813 establishments in England]]\n[[Category:Locks on the River Thames]]\n", "name_user": "John of Reading", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200etop:Typo fixing, replaced: Pharoah \u2192 Pharaoh to match the linked article", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shepperton_Lock"}
